# SASS/SCSS installation steps (Node + npm)

1) Install NVM (Node Version Manager)
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   # close terminal, reopen (or run: source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh)

2) Install Node.js 20.16.0 (recommended)
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0
   node -v
   npm -v

3) Install Sass compiler (project local)
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss
   npm init -y
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4

4) Compile examples (from this directory)
   npx sass 0-debug_log.scss
   npx sass 1-color_variable.scss
   npx sass 2-nested_tag.scss
   npx sass 3-mixin_margins.scss
